name: Plugins Management - No "Remove" option for pre-packaged plugins

customFields.Priority P1 to P4: P3 - Deep Functions (Do extensive scenarios work?)

inline.description:
Plugins Management - No "Remove" option for pre-packaged plugins
————————————————————————————
  1. System Console ➜ Plugins ➜ Management
  2. Scroll down and locate "Jira (pre-packaged)" and "Zoom (pre-packaged)" plugins
inline.expectedResult: • You should not see an option to "Remove" these plugins as they are pre-packaged and will be reinstalled on server restart
